{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"我们该怎样回答","authors":["柯岩"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":4,"day":21}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们该怎样回答"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柯岩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在年轻战士的墓前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我放下一束洁白的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洁白的鲜花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要把后方的感激、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"崇敬和欢欣……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带给他——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都带给他……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陡地一阵轻风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浸透我的肺腑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直扑我的面颊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"墓侧小树的枝丫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一起摇曳，树叶沙沙……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，好象在向我致意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又象在和我说话——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“他用胸膛堵住的枪眼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——早已喑哑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还击途中的重重碉堡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——也全部摧垮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东方的古巴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已受到应有的惩罚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“第三军事强国”的“勇士”们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也早已丢盔弃甲……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他尽了一个战士的最高职责，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同志，同志，你知道吗？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦，是的，是的，可——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们该怎样回答？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“硝烟，炮火……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暂时都已远去，远去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他所在连队的战友"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也已整队回原地驻扎……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国，到处是孩子的欢笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"边境的弹坑里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也重新开放出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朵朵鲜艳的小花……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他是满心欢喜地长眠地下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同志，同志，你明白吗？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦，是的，是的，可——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们该怎样回答？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“他的心还在地下跳动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日日夜夜催我快快长大……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我伸枝展叶直上蓝天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让白云托住我的枝枝丫丫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好在云端远远眺望——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的高山、流水；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问候祖国的乡村、城镇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那每一户人家……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同志，同志，你想到吗？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦，是的，是的，可——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们该怎样回答？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“他问油田又搭起多少新的井架，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他问电力又增加了多少千瓦；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他问城里的居民楼又多了几幢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他问地里可长满丰收的庄稼？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他急着想看见——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四个现代化计算中心的蓝图，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"后方的人们是怎样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在祖国的大地上描画。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同志，同志，你懂得吗？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦，是的，是的，可——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们该怎样回答？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“他问，他特别地问呵——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和他同辈的青年在干什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们的学习好不好？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们前进的步伐大不大？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些曾被“四人帮”砍伤的心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在积极治疗吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是否已结上了痊愈的伤疤？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他说——他说——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他特别思念他们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为他把自己未尽的生命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一并溶进了他们青春的年华……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因此，他问，他不停地问——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同志，同志，你听见吗？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦，是的，我听见了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全——听——见——啦！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在年轻战士的墓前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我放下一束洁白的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洁白的鲜花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我仰望那伸枝展叶的小树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伴着泪水和感激，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用我笨拙的笔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记下了他所有的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思念、关怀和问话——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦，同志，我年轻的朋友，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你听见吗？你听见吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我亲爱的同志们哪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们该怎样回答？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦，是的，是的，我们——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"该——怎——样——回答？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九七九年三—四月广西—北京"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}